587
01:10:04.208 --> 01:10:05.666
Wait!

588
01:10:06.291 --> 01:10:07.541
Come on.

589
01:10:08.541 --> 01:10:09.416
Where should we go?

590
01:10:09.500 --> 01:10:11.291
- Look down!
- Mom!

591
01:10:14.666 --> 01:10:15.958
Shut up!

592
01:10:21.541 --> 01:10:23.208
Oh God...

593
01:10:23.291 --> 01:10:25.541
