626
01:15:20.291 --> 01:15:21.875
<i>Butterfly</i>

627
01:15:23.916 --> 01:15:25.916
<i>Wailing and moaning</i>

628
01:15:29.833 --> 01:15:32.458
<i>Wherever my moon has gone</i>

629
01:15:36.833 --> 01:15:38.750
<i>Let my wings</i>

630
01:15:39.875 --> 01:15:41.666
