733
01:22:38.958 --> 01:22:41.375
<i>You can use your own words to pray.</i>

734
01:22:41.458 --> 01:22:44.291
<i>Ask permission from Salim's ancestors</i>

735
01:22:44.375 --> 01:22:46.166
<i>and pray</i>

736
01:22:46.250 --> 01:22:49.958
<i>that their souls find peace
and that they will watch over us.</i>

737
01:22:51.500 --> 01:22:53.583
<i>Salim, Febri,</i>

738
01:22:53.666 --> 01:22:55.541
<i>go to Mei Hwa's grave</i>

739
01:22:55.625 --> 01:22:58.583
<i>and dig up her body.</i>

740
01:22:58.666 --> 01:23:01.166
<i>Be careful. Bring the body back here.</i>

741
01:23:01.250 --> 01:23:04.750
<i>Make sure you bring
their wedding rings as well.</i>

742
01:23:04.833 --> 01:23:08.166
<i>The wedding rings are immensely important.</i>

743
01:23:08.250 --> 01:23:09.958
<i>Don't forget that.</i>

744
