01:27:02.416 --> 01:27:04.000
Bhanu!

785
01:27:04.791 --> 01:27:07.791
Febri, where's Salim? Febri, damn it!

786
01:27:07.875 --> 01:27:09.375
What's wrong with you?

787
01:27:09.458 --> 01:27:10.791
You...

788
01:27:10.875 --> 01:27:12.333
